section_title: 23a01 - Newspaper devoted to court news and legal notices.
text:
A daily publication which contains
news of the local courts, legal notices, other matters pertaining to court
proceedings, and advertisements is a newspaper within the meaning of the Sec
13(a)(8) exemption.
